title: Jazz Master Randy Weston In Conversation with Music Historian Willard Jenkins - April 8, 2011
description: Jazz Master Randy Weston in conversation with music historian Willard Jenkins. This event took place at Sankofa Video Books & Cafe on April 8, 2011. Drums led by Jabari Exum and featuring Malari Moore and Dante Pope.
